Project Summary -
In this project it is shown about all the information about the bookings of the Hotel. hotel booking dataset can help you explore those questions! 
This data set contains booking information for a city hotel and a resort hotel, and includes information such as when the booking was made,
length of stay, the number of adults, children, and/or babies, and the number of available parking spaces, among other things.
Problem Statement
Have you ever wondered when the best time of year to book a hotel room is? Or the optimal length of stay in order to get the best daily rate? 
What if you wanted to predict whether or not a hotel was likely to receive a disproportionately high number of special requests?

This hotel booking dataset can help you explore those questions! This data set contains booking information for a city hotel and a resort hotel
, and includes information such as when the booking was made, length of stay, the number of adults, children, and/or babies, and the number of available parking spaces, among other things. 


